

Needed pages:
    A home Page.
       - Where the user can view all songs.
    A login page.
        = WHere the user can login.
    A signup Page.
        - Where the user can signup
    A song creation page.
        - Where the user can create a song with the song image and name and audio.
    A playlist creation page.
        - Where the user can create a playlist with the playlist image and name.
    A playlist page.
        - Where the user can view a playlist and play the playlists songs.
    

Song folder Structure:
    `
    - /public/songs/
        - /song1_Id/
            -/song1_audio.mp3
            -/song1_image.png
            -/song1_info.json
        - /song2_Id/
            -/song2_audio.mp3
            -/song2_image.png
            -/song2_info.json
    `
